author: blazetrooper501
title: AWSOME
review: This set is cool and pretty rare the only way to get one was attending celebration V.They were sold for $80 and only 2000 ever made they are more of a display piece and not to play with.I got both of mine signed If you are looking for this set go to ebay and type in lego cube dude and you will find it good luck on trying to get them.
